# Cell Компонент ячейки. Props (свойства) для компонента Cell: [{"name":"view","type":{"name":"enum","raw":"\"default\"","value":[{"value":"\"default\""}]}},{"name":"size","type":{"name":"enum","raw":"\"m\" | \"s\" | \"l\" | \"xs\"","value":[{"value":"\"m\""},{"value":"\"s\""},{"value":"\"l\""},{"value":"\"xs\""}]}},{"name":"contentLeft","type":{"name":"ReactNode"}},{"name":"contentRight","type":{"name":"ReactNode"}},{"name":"alignContentLeft","type":{"name":"enum","raw":"AlignProp","value":[{"value":"\"center\""},{"value":"\"top\""},{"value":"\"bottom\""}]}},{"name":"alignContentRight","type":{"name":"enum","raw":"AlignProp","value":[{"value":"\"center\""},{"value":"\"top\""},{"value":"\"bottom\""}]}},{"name":"stretching","type":{"name":"enum","raw":"\"filled\" | \"fixed\" | \"auto\"","value":[{"value":"\"filled\""},{"value":"\"fixed\""},{"value":"\"auto\""}]}},{"name":"content","type":{"name":"ReactNode"}},{"name":"description","type":{"name":"string"}},{"name":"title","type":{"name":"string"}},{"name":"subtitle","type":{"name":"string"}},{"name":"label","type":{"name":"string"}}] Компонент представляет собой стилизировные слоты для контента. Также имеются вспомогательные компоненты ( Textbox, TextTitle, TextSubtitle, TextLabel ). Они представляют собой стилизированный текст и слот для них. ## Примеры ### Базовое использование ```tsx
